---
title: Charred Corn & Rainbow Trout Salad with Peaches, Feta and Spiced Honey Vinaigrette
description: Charring corn and peaches stovetop is a great trick for creating a grilled flavour indoors! The sweet and earthy combination of honey, balsamic and our spice blend is sure to - ahem - spice up your life! (Or at least, your dinner.)
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/-45a67579.jpg
